description:
TPO 247 A1
T601 Black Poplar - Crown reduce by 20-25%; T603 Leyland Cypress - Fell to ground level; G607 1 No. Hornbeam, 1 No. Oak & 1 No. Birch - Re-Coppice; T610 White Poplar - Crown reduce by 25%; T616 Leyland Cypress - Fell to ground level; T618 White Poplar - Crown reduce by 20-25%; G625 4 No Elm - Fell; G628 3 No. Leyland Cypress - Reduce in height by 3.0 metres; G629 Elm and Norway Maple - Thin group by felling marked trees; T633 Norway Maple - Fell to ground level; A1 Hawthorn, Damson & Elder - Thin by 50%; G638 Norway Maple - Fell to ground level; A2 Field Maple, Norway Maple & Elm - Thin group by 50%. Fell all Elm; A3 White Willow, Blackthorn, Poplar, Elm & Goat Willow - Fell all Elm. Coppice Goat Willow. Thin Blackthorn by 50%; T640 White Willow - Crown reduce by 20-25%; T641 White Willow - Crown reduce by 20-25%; G642 Leyland Cypress, Hazel, Elm & Hawthorn - Fell marked trees. Fell all Elm. Cut back all vegetation to clear boundary by 3.0 metres; T646 White Willow - Prune to clear building by 4.0 metres; A5 Hawthorn, Sycamore, Ash, Bramble & Conifers - Thin area by 50%. Prune back from boundary by 3.0 metres and over road to clear fence line; A6 Ash, Elm, Dogwood, Hazel, Field Maple & Bramble - Coppice Hazel. Cut back Bramble. Fell all Elm; G648 Oak, Cherry, Field Maple & Birch - Thin Group by 50%. Prune back from boundary by 3.0 metres; G650 4 No. Cherry - Fell marked trees; A7 Mixed broadleaf trees - Thin group by 50%. Prune back from boundary by 3.0 metres; T651 Birch - Prune back from road by 2.0 metres; T652 Birch - Prune back from road by 2.0 metres; T655 Birch - Fell to ground level; T661 Birch - Fell to ground level; T675 Birch - Remove adjacent Goat Willow; T676 Birch - Remove adjacent Goat Willow; G678 3 No. Cherry - Fell to ground level; T680 Alder - Fell to ground level; T681 Alder - Fell Alder, Fell adjacent dead tree and Goat Willow
